{"tid":1749891,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【TVB 獨家，止暴制亂選舉廣告】+ 每日洗版任務 - 美麗華旅遊","createTime":"2019-11-24T07:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T10:57:46.000Z","uid":113630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18cf196e81b2cedb0e8111a93679e6df393744a3","tid":1749891,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB 播放「止暴制亂」選舉廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大量TVB偽員、護旗手參與</span></strong></span> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MFAofficeHK/videos/979333199104158/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMFAofficeHK%2Fvideos%2F979333199104158%2F&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=3987648b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MFAofficeHK/videos/979333199104158/</a> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">//【成龍、容祖兒、陳小春等數十港星齊發聲：用選票向暴力說不！】 <br />\n明天就是區議會選舉投票的日子。對關心香港未來的人來說，這是一個以票止暴、挽救香港不容錯過的機會。為此，成龍、惠英紅、王祖藍、容祖兒、陳小春等數十名香港知名藝人站了出來，為香港加油打氣，呼籲大家用選票踢走暴力，保護家園。<br />\n 「香港你我家，建設靠大家！」「重新出發，重建我們認識的香港！」<br />\n「拒絕暴力，守護香港！」 <br />\n止暴制亂需要你的寶貴一票！//</span>  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<br />\n抗爭要堅持，屌柒TVB成習慣 <br />\n只需每日幾秒，救助被洗腦藍絲&amp;老豆老母</span></strong></span> <br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong> <br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n5. tag 多幾個friend做任  <br />\n<br />\n之前我哋呼籲過網民洗美麗華旅遊版兩次，但佢哋仍然無視訴求，hide曬啲我哋嘅請願留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。唔緊要！我哋轉場去美麗華廣場洗板，等總公司回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！  <br />\n是日精選@24 Nov 2019  <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>美麗華旅遊</strong></span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/miraplacehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmiraplacehk%2F&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=f7e02e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/miraplacehk/</a></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※留言template，美麗華特別版</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n <blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！美麗華旅遊無視網民訴求，故要求美麗華集團回應。本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時抵制恆基集團旗下品牌。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCmCGX3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCmCGX3.png&h=67e319c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">應該過咗今日先load到圖</span><br />\n  <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span> <br />\n美麗華旅遊臭史：<br />\n 1️⃣隱瞞燃油附加費減左價，收多顧客錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n違反商品說明條例罪成，係旅行社中第一間 <br />\n美麗華真係業界翹楚呀！欺騙港人實在功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n2️⃣母公司恒基：撐送中、撐特首、撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣告部經理Sindy Kwong：無視港人繼續喺TVB落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總經理李振庭：提名777做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深藍高層Eva Chan：大鬧法官撤示威者控罪係法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 3️⃣破產董事陳若磐：傻佬學人搞生意，玩爛永安旅遊，之後轉埸美麗華旅遊。搞到公司2017年違反商品說明條例罪成。<br />\n佢最愛TVB姐仔，溝到開埋房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係情迷TVB 💚💙❤️  <br />\n<br />\n全面杯葛美麗華旅遊！等到佢破產！ <br />\n<br />\n [Source] <br />\n瞞減燃附費多收錢 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36tuCBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36tuCBE&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=799d5c4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/36tuCBE</a> <br />\n開房記 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/339hiQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F339hiQs&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=d6b79e57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/339hiQs</a> <br />\n支持《逃犯條例》修訂 bit.do/faUTB <br />\n恒地發聲明撐特首撐警 bit.do/faUTM  <br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFB5XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFB5XW.jpg&h=34f0d91a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仲有大量圖喺後面</strong></span></span>   <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span>  <br />\n消費前諗清楚  <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=004927f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>    <br />\n－－－－－－－  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong>  <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=7390423c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a> <br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb  <br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=37e8a478\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a> <br />\nTG 抵制綜合組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=4014556b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a> <br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=679393eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"3bba9dcadff2f37c43438691a6fce774af445694","tid":1749891,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87adb889add8fb2c53598165ff34afc0ce9d5ad0","tid":1749891,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tU7FFKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtU7FFKd.jpg&h=775644bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/225LRQU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F225LRQU.png&h=90685065&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UEuHT4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUEuHT4f.png&h=2eed2b10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1WWd4g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1WWd4g.png&h=94d4a322&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uj4AuCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https